article_title: Poll: Think you know Obamacare? Take our quiz to find out
article_text:
Monday is the last day to sign up for health insurance through Covered California, the state’s health insurance exchange. More than one million people have signed up for coverage since enrollment began six months ago.

Do you understand the basic elements of your own health insurance, and the federal healthcare law? Take our quiz to find out.

Quiz: Are you an Obamacare expert?
